Usage:

1. start jboss as 7(version 7.1.0.Final as tested) with Java Enterprise 
   Edition 6 full profile preview, which includes the technology preview 
   of Java API for REST (JAX-RX):
   
   $JBOSS_HOME/bin/./standalone.sh --server-config=standalone-preview.xml


2. run btm:
   mvn clean install jboss-as:deploy


3. go to http://localhost:8080/savara-btm/
   upload a xml bpmn2 file, click "Upload", the corresponding json format
   will be returned.
   (a simple bpmn2 created by eclipse bpmn2 editor can be found in 
    /src/main/resources folder)
